snippet.title: QUACK ATTACK 1985 ORIGINAL GAME REVEAL TRAILER
snippet.description:
UPDATE! QUACK ATTACK 1985: TURBO DX EDITION IS NOW LIVE! CHECK IT OUT AT WWW.ATTACKMOUNTAIN.COM !

It's non-stop arcade madness for computer machine with QUACK ATTACK 1985! Duckster's finally had enough of those damned geese; retribution is nigh. Five unique game modes, crazy visuals and an epic showdown, all set to the music of Jake 'virt' Kaufman.
